" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n舉過一排<br />\n覺得都冇咩效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22499dc603a8ebd1ef9fea6ca14ca89983f8b841","tid":102534,"uid":76167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:35:12.000Z","msg":"女仔做gym好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83a4df274375b936c05662760f50a27aad9580d0","tid":102534,"uid":80015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:48:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.tpsports.com.tw/templates/cache/6247/images/products/photooriginal-6247-268910.jpg?91988\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tpsports.com.tw%2Ftemplates%2Fcache%2F6247%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2Fphotooriginal-6247-268910.jpg%3F91988&h=a1fe25d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n練橫d個背, 條腰睇落會突出d  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我已經38膊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪唔需要再玩呢個？</blockquote><br />\n覺得夠做下腳囉, 女仔屎忽有肉很多仔昅的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做腳係咪淨係squat?</blockquote><br />\n主要係squat囉 , 想邊個部位有線條d, 咪做返相對動作(呢句好廢) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb74e997d9e7ab7243955e1a09b0236f9d3b94b3","tid":102534,"uid":80015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:58:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果之前有做開減過又肥返，有去做gym想7月前減到40磅做咩最好效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一星期有3到4日做</blockquote><br />\n減肥一定係做帶氧, 不過負重可以增加肌肉,即係每日所需既熱量都會增加, 減完之後冇咁易反彈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 最快既減肥方法就係帶氧+負重+控制飲食三管齊下 <br />\n控制飲食唔係叫你唔食野, 食d少糖少油 or gi值低既食物, 情況許可可以少食多餐, 一日5,6餐隔2~3個鐘食一次, 食到岩岩好飽肚就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac74e981c5643143cd42760541e76b20ce07980b","tid":102534,"uid":80015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T11:01:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女仔做gym好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自從做左gym, d瘦猛猛, 筷子腳既女仔就睇唔上眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b2b66cefb40aabffd964c4a3fd609b23f4bcf2","tid":102534,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T15:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d328774f593ac2a1248640ed83a699dfa826a695","tid":102534,"uid":17134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T15:10:55.000Z","msg":"想減40磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇過一休，都係諗住做咗負重之後先再做帶氧<br />\n同埋會打泰拳<br />\n我覺得磅數已經唔重要，係體態問題<br />\n不過驚康文署個啲太多人<br />\n同埋幾年無去會唔會無咗record<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c7b4c05a99a261a9aef1a683b366ac5bc81bb6","tid":102534,"uid":80327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T15:20:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我已經38膊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪唔需要再玩呢個？</blockquote><br />\n覺得夠做下腳囉, 女仔屎忽有肉很多仔昅的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做腳係咪淨係squat?</blockquote><br />\nDeadlift都重要"},{"pid":"bf3e387fa4abf02ec5bace9be2ff5c1945cdf5c7","tid":102534,"uid":52824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r